Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(1822,75)\fn@MS Gothic\frz270}オマエも泳者！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.63,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(1852,400)\fn@MS Gothic\frz270}プレイヤー
